== Organizer == v. 1
That will be simple application which might be used to organize tasks and schedules.
This is first part and whole thing is not finished yet.

== GOALS AND FUNCTIONALITY ==
Application should be helpfull to organize programmers work for small size projects.

----------------------------
Short Structure of organizer:
Each project has many group of tasks and each of them has_many tasks

Example:

I. Project:
  1. group of task
    a.task
    b.task

  2. group of task
    d.task
    e.task
----------------------------

Application uses CSS blueprint framework

